<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>We've Received Your Inquiry</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4A5568;
            background-color: #FAFAFC;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5E60CE 0%, #56CFE1 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #718096;
            background-color: #F7FAFC;
        }
        .footer-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer-links a {
            color: #5E60CE;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://forecastly.online/template/img/forecastly_logo_64x64.png" width="24px" height="24px" alt="Forecastly" style="border:0; display:inline-block;" />
            <span>Forecastly</span>
        </div>
        <h2>We've Received Your Message</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{ contactSupport.fullName }},</p>

        <p>Thank you for contacting Forecastly Support! We've successfully received your inquiry and will get back to you shortly.</p>

        <p><strong>Your Inquiry Details:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Subject:</strong> {{ contactSupport.title }}</li>
            <li><strong>Message:</strong> {{ contactSupport.description }}</li>
            <li><strong>Submitted:</strong> {{ contactSupport.createdAt|date('F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A') }}</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Forecastly,<br>The Forecastly Support Team</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Forecastly by Meridian Wealth Technologies, LLC. All rights reserved.</p>

        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="{{ url('privacy_policy') }}">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="{{ url('terms_of_service') }}">Terms of Service</a>
        </div>

        <p>Meridian Wealth Technologies, LLC<br>
            600 West Broadway Suite 700-100A PMB 70148<br>
            San Diego, CA 92101</p>

        <p><em>This is a transactional email. You're receiving this because you contacted Forecastly support.</em></p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>